{"tid":1323301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉嫌咬斷警員手指案押後至9月再訊　被告獲准保釋","createTime":"2019-07-16T07:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T13:53:33.000Z","uid":275588,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ffb2efef368a3b3c04fd0d0599870592a4b612","tid":1323301,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:59:04.000Z","msg":"一名22歲男子星期日在沙田新城市廣場發生的警民衝突中，涉嫌咬斷一名警員的手指，被控兩項蓄意傷人，一項襲警及一項未能出示身份證明文件罪，下午在沙田裁判法院提堂。案件押後至9月10日再訊，被告獲准以一萬元保釋，定時到田心警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n被告杜啟華報稱學生，被控本月14日晚上約10時，在沙田新城市廣場襲擊警員葉卓軒，同時被控有意圖而非法及惡意傷害高級警司梁子健和偵緝警長梁啟業，以及未能出示身份證明文件。<br />\n<br />\n聆訊實施特別座位安排，除預留傳媒座位，其餘80個座位以先到先得形式分配給公眾人士。現場所見，旁聽席滿座，公眾人士站滿庭內通道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468652-20190716.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468652-20190716.htm&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=d075561f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468652-20190716.htm&h=deb2bbd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468652-20190716.htm</a>"},{"pid":"44af9bcf233ec86508def022be0b0b7e5d1cbee9","tid":1323301,"uid":238051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:59:44.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"35bbacf7bb6f261e286287468685e95513fde860","tid":1323301,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hk