hk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468652-20190716.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"[廢老文宣]第二戰場係電台呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1323274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1323274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f79046d977cd5b06d05270d79551d0153bca7b7b","tid":1323301,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabefe5bbaa0962793e28cfeb07e64c7c6d018d8","tid":1323301,"uid":186338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"595f31e44848e38e542e036aeca70d3e6dae68c5","tid":1323301,"uid":57723,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"叫佢宜家買機票飛加拿大<br />\n做政治難民好過坐冤獄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:34:16.000Z","msg":"保緊唔可以離境"},{"pid":"8f0cc3c97c1e7c19975e011d995d96865acf8960","tid":1323301,"uid":281309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f52ebf2c89f7d4f649815734f9dcbea4bdff0e1e","tid":1323301,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:36:22.000Z","msg":"有無人搵到片幫佢？"},{"pid":"57942faf9cc1875b36c5ebef82cbc9f35d6dcd78","tid":1323301,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10c0cdf1087259b36c71441a38859e3dbb721cd4","tid":1323301,"uid":249347,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"e8c340112569a5f9f443d391a3a0f07542545495","tid":1323301,"uid":160592,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"是日笑話<br />\n未能出示身份證明文件罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁成堆黑警都冇委任證喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"𠵱家係只畀州官放火，唔畀百姓點燈"},{"pid":"c075126e633bf4f2a40a6589f3aa999fbd18541d","tid":1323301,"uid":249347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57942faf9cc1875b36c5